---
import ProjectLayout from "../../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro";
---

<ProjectLayout
  title="Eastern Edge Robotics"
  subtitle="Software/Electrical Team · Sep 2024 – Present"
  logo="/logos/eastern-edge.png"
  logoAlt="Eastern Edge Robotics"
  context="Team"
  tags={["C++", "CANBus", "RS-485", "Raspberry Pi", "OnShape", "3D Printing"]}
>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-600 text-white/80 mb-4">Overview</h2>
    <p class="text-white/55 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      Eastern Edge Robotics is a student-run team at Memorial University that designs, builds, 
      and operates underwater remotely operated vehicles (ROVs) for international competition 
      in marine environments. I contribute to both the software and electrical subsystems.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-600 text-white/80 mb-6">What I Built</h2>
    <div class="space-y-8">

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h3 class="font-display font-600 text-white/85 mb-2">Mechanical Design & Fabrication</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Directed the design and fabrication of mechanical assemblies for the underwater ROV 
          using OnShape and 3D printing, improving maintainability and reliability under 
          field conditions in marine environments.
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-dashed border-white/10 p-8 text-center text-sm text-white/25 font-mono">
          Add photos: ROV assembly, 3D printed parts, OnShape models
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h3 class="font-display font-600 text-white/85 mb-2">Electrical Integration</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Assembled and integrated electrical and mechanical subsystems — soldering, crimping, 
          heat-shrinking — troubleshooting issues during testing to ensure field-ready 
          performance.
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-dashed border-white/10 p-8 text-center text-sm text-white/25 font-mono">
          Add photos: wiring, integration, testing
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h3 class="font-display font-600 text-white/85 mb-2">Communication Protocols & Embedded Software</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
          Investigating CANBus/RS-485 communication protocols, assisting in hardware test 
          automation, and writing embedded C++ on Raspberry Pi 4 to support efficient ROV 
          subsystem control.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</ProjectLayout>